  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Escape Z, the thrilling multiplayer survival game where you and your friends must join forces to face off against ever-growing hordes of flesh-hungry zombies. Get ready for an intense, adrenaline-fuelled challenge as you try to survive as long as possible in a post-apocalyptic world overrun by the zombie plague.<br>⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀    <h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><br><br><strong>Tactical Cooperation :</strong> Collaborate with other players in matches of up to 4 people. Plan tactics to survive waves of increasingly vicious zombies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/5737b960fa9b60e2fd123e804205de2a.poster.avif?t=1767522010\" width=558 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/5737b960fa9b60e2fd123e804205de2a.webm?t=1767522010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/5737b960fa9b60e2fd123e804205de2a.mp4?t=1767522010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Different Character :</strong> Choose up to 8 characters with different initial weapons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/24e9e44443f8345247745abd25836133.poster.avif?t=1767522010\" width=558 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/24e9e44443f8345247745abd25836133.webm?t=1767522010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/24e9e44443f8345247745abd25836133.mp4?t=1767522010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Dynamic Maps :</strong> Explore several detailed maps, each with unique locations. From desolate ruined city streets to haunted forests, each map will require <br>different strategies to survive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/00b37cc76faa73944982e30596310f51.poster.avif?t=1767522010\" width=558 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/00b37cc76faa73944982e30596310f51.webm?t=1767522010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/00b37cc76faa73944982e30596310f51.mp4?t=1767522010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Special Enemies:</strong> Face special enemies. Prepare to think quickly and strategically to defeat these unique threats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/e61fa6c811391caab5865fe2c97dc7ad.poster.avif?t=1767522010\" width=558 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/e61fa6c811391caab5865fe2c97dc7ad.webm?t=1767522010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/e61fa6c811391caab5865fe2c97dc7ad.mp4?t=1767522010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get ready for an explosive and fast-paced multiplayer gaming experience in Escape Z. Assemble your team, hone your skills and prepare to fight for survival in a zombie-infested world.",
