 several detailed maps, each with unique locations. From desolate ruined city streets to haunted forests, each map will require <br>different strategies to survive.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/00b37cc76faa73944982e30596310f51.poster.avif?t=1767522010\" width=558 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/00b37cc76faa73944982e30596310f51.webm?t=1767522010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/00b37cc76faa73944982e30596310f51.mp4?t=1767522010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Special Enemies:</strong> Face special enemies. Prepare to think quickly and strategically to defeat these unique threats.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/e61fa6c811391caab5865fe2c97dc7ad.poster.avif?t=1767522010\" width=558 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/e61fa6c811391caab5865fe2c97dc7ad.webm?t=1767522010\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2571140/extras/e61fa6c811391caab5865fe2c97dc7ad.mp4?t=1767522010\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get ready for an explosive and fast-paced multiplayer gaming experience in Escape Z. Assemble your team, hone your skills and prepare to fight for survival in a zombie-infested world.",
